@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - US116

actor "Maintenance Technician" as User
participant "System" as System

activate User


User -> System : Authenticate User
activate System
System --> User : Authentication Successful (Token JWT)
deactivate System


User -> System : logMaintenanceActivity(aircraftReg, templateId, date, technicians, status, notes)
activate System


System --> User : Inform Success (201 Created + Activity Data)
System --> User : Error (400 Bad Request / 404 Not Found)
deactivate System

deactivate User
@enduml